embeds.title: Help
embeds.description:
If you find yourself using this, chances are you've hit a roadblock! Don't worryâ€”I'm here to assist you!

To begin, if you're tweaking a message, use **ModifyMessage**. This needs both a true or false value and the text value. If either is missing, it won't function! If it's true, it will reset everything with your provided text; if false, it will append your text.

Now, let's talk about **ModifyAttachment**. This only needs the attachment/parameter! If you already have an image, it will replace it with the new one. If there's no image at all, it will add one.

There is also a **DeleteAttachment** option using this will simply delete the attachment!

Introducing **ModifyMessageColor**. Simply provide the hex code as the text value. If there's no existing color, it will assign one for you. Easy as pie!

**RemoveMessageColor** does the same as **DeleteAttachment** just removing the color from the message!

**ApplyTag**: This function adds your search to a specified tag. Please ensure that the tag already exists. Conversely, **RemoveTag** removes a tag from your search. Use the text command parameter to pick a tag!

**DuplicateSearch** will duplicate any search! Insert the search name under title and the new name under text!

**ModifyThumbnail** and **ModifyAttatchment** will only accept tenor or imgur links. These can be gotten by right clicking the image or gif and copying image address!
```
https://i.imgur.com/
```
```
https://c.tenor.com/
```
```
https://media1.tenor.com/m/
```
